name: Look At Me
overview:
Look At Me is a daily internet magazine, which they create together with their readers. Today daily traffic of the site is about 90 thousands of people. That’s more than 1 000 000 unique visitors per month. Every day the editors and the users of Look At Me write about 40 materials about fashion, music, design, modern art, cinema, technologies and entertainments of big city and add more than 100 events and 20 photo galleries.

The Village (www.the-village.ru) is a daily supplement about cultural and public life of Moscow city - entertainments, services, food and people

FurFur (www.lookatme.ru/furfur) is a daily supplement for men about fashion, drinks, arts and women
